So we're thrilled
that all of you

00:00:43.130 --> 00:00:46.280
are here for this special
guest and this special evening.

00:00:46.280 --> 00:00:48.950
Before I introduce them, there
are a few other quick things

00:00:48.950 --> 00:00:50.000
I do want to say.

