You know, when you do
these kind of events

00:02:51.120 --> 00:02:54.252
and you sometimes say someone
needs no introduction, well,

00:02:54.252 --> 00:02:56.460
literally, if you looked in
a dictionary Doris Kearns

00:02:56.460 --> 00:02:59.490
Goodwin's picture would be there
in the need no introduction.

