This is her seventh
book and it draws

00:03:09.210 --> 00:03:14.160
on her five decades of amazing
scholarship that she's done.

00:03:14.160 --> 00:03:15.830
And her awards and
recognitions, I'm

00:03:15.830 --> 00:03:17.580
not going to list them
all because we have

00:03:17.580 --> 00:03:18.960
an important forum to get to.

00:03:18.960 --> 00:03:22.170
But a few of them include
