has won so many
distinguished awards

00:03:43.890 --> 00:03:46.980
during her 25
years in journalism

00:03:46.980 --> 00:03:49.890
both at PUR and at
NPR Here and Now.

00:03:49.890 --> 00:03:53.100
She's won a Peabody
and several Emmys.

00:03:53.100 --> 00:03:56.790
She has previously done work
with NBC and CBS and the Today

00:03:56.790 --> 00:03:57.320
show.

00:03:57.320 --> 00:03:58.320
Again, it's a long list.

00:03:58.320 --> 00:04:00.752
So join, me when I
say it's a real honor

00:04:00.752 --> 00:04:02.460
to have both of these
women here tonight.

00:04:02.460 --> 00:04:02.960
Thank you.

00:04:02.960 --> 00:04:04.798
