The right wing
websites while crowing

00:11:29.695 --> 00:11:31.820
about how we couldn't have
written better ourselves

00:11:31.820 --> 00:11:33.695
and couldn't have done
this better ourselves.

00:11:33.695 --> 00:11:35.870
So that is happening.

00:11:35.870 --> 00:11:38.630
Frightening time
for a lot of people.

